{
  "texts": [
    "In comparison, artificial neural networks (ANN) are utilized for classification.",
    "The proposed method is evaluated using the PH2 dataset, which consists of 200 dermoscopic images with 40 melanoma and 160 non-melanoma images, and the HAM10000 dataset, which is part of the ISIC 2018 challenge.",
    "On the HAM10000 and PH2 datasets, the proposed model achieves 94.9% and 98.0% accuracy, respectively.",
    "Shetty et al.",
    "[43] proposed a model that applies data augmentation on the dataset to enhance the model's precision."
  ]
}